Our History
HM Capital Management was founded in 2005 but its roots date back much further as its founders previously worked as a team at a major brokerage firm. The decision to form HM Capital Management was an easy one as our focus has always been to provide the highest level of professional advice on a fee-only basis with no products to sell. In short, we wanted to serve our clients as a legal fiduciary. This was no longer an option working at a brokerage firm and therefore the decision to start HM Capital Management was formulated.
Since inception, HM Capital Management has experienced considerable growth and has expanded in both professional expertise and client assets. In 2010, InvestmentNews recognized HM Capital Management as a “Top 40 Fee-Only Registered Investment Advisor” as well as a “Top 20 Fee-Only Emerging Registered Investment Adviser.”  In 2016 HM Capital Management was named in the Top Wealth Managers & Financial Advisors in St. Louis by AdvisoryHQ.com.  While such recognition is gratifying, our focus remains on providing unbiased, fee-only advice with our own corporate growth as a byproduct.










