								Meet the Firm							








Mission & Core Values
Open


Our mission is to be problem solvers, a source of solutions and the go-to persons for all things financial. At HM Capital Management this is accomplished by providing fee-only investment advice from a team of experienced professionals that is always serving in the best interest of the client.




Close


Our Culture
At HM Capital Management we stress teamwork in everything we do. While individual creativity is always encouraged, we have found that team effort often produces the best results. While the old way may still be the best way, we encourage creativity and imagination because we are constantly striving to find better solutions to clients’ problems.
At HM Capital Management we regularly receive confidential information as part of our normal client relationships. To breach a confidence or to use confidential information improperly would be unthinkable. We understand times do change, but core professional ethics and values do not go into or out of fashion.
At HM Capital Management we believe personal modesty, social reserve, and deliberate absence of arrogance are characteristics of great professional cultures. HM Capital Management is a culture of strong individuals absent of egotism.
At HM Capital Management we believe the people at great firms work harder than their competitors-both longer, more demanding days and more days and nights each week. While producing more, they also insist on producing at the highest quality.  They take pride and find great meaning in what they and their firm can achieve for clients. The dedication of our people to the firm and the intense effort they give their jobs are greater than one finds in most other organizations.  We think that is an important part of our success.












