For the second year in a row HM Capital Management has been named one of the Top 9 Financial Advisors in St. Louis by Advisor HQ, a financial review and news website. HM Capital Management was recognized as a fee-only RIA who serves as a fiduciary to their clients and staffed by a qualified team of professionals with a range of certifications.  “It is an honor to be recognized for the second year in a row” said Matt Kopsky, President of HM Capital Management. Matt Kopsky went on to say, “At HM Capital Management we strive to be advocates for our client’s peace of mind and celebrate a culture where our clients come first.”







