As Senior Vice President, Ben is responsible for overseeing the day-to-day needs of Family Advisory and Institutional clients.

Ben has achieved the Certified Public Accountant, Personal Financial Specialist, and CERTIFIED FINANCIAL PLANNER™ certifications. The AICPA’s Personal Financial Specialist credential is granted exclusively to CPAs with the combination of extensive tax expertise and comprehensive knowledge of financial planning.
